Rental room agents have many duties and responsibilities, including:
Customer service: Answering questions, resolving issues, and providing ongoing support
Reservations: Taking bookings, explaining rental terms, and ensuring accurate return policies.
Paperwork: Completing paperwork, updating records, and taking payments
Inventory: Managing inventory, promoting upgrades, and assisting with emergencies
Vehicle condition: Recording a car's condition, checking mileage, and inspecting for damage
Customer experience: Greeting customers, showing them to their vehicle, and pointing out special features
Sales: Providing sales support to regular business accounts
Education: Educating customers on car models
Car rental agents may also perform call-backs to check customer satisfaction.

